OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to schoolgirl who
OL,4,Cdied following house fire
OL,6,FThe family of a schoolgirl with "an
OL,7,Finfectious energy and a heart full of
OL,8,Flove" who died following a house fire
OL,9,Fhave paid tribute to her.
OL,11,FLayla Allen, 13, died after the fire
OL,12,Fbroke out in a bedroom at the home in
OL,13,FPrescot, Knowsley on 2 April.
OL,15,FA man, woman and five children were
OL,16,Fable to escape from the home unharmed,
OL,17,FMerseyside Police said.
