OL,6,FThe force is now investigating,
OL,7,Falongside Merseyside Fire and Rescue
OL,8,FService, to establish the cause of the
OL,9,Ffire, it added.
OL,11,FIn a tribute to the teenager, Layla's
OL,12,Ffamily said she was a "typical, happy,
OL,13,Fand full-of-life 13-year-old".
OL,15,F"Layla was a shining light in the
OL,16,Flives of everyone who knew her," they
OL,17,Fsaid in a statement.
