OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to schoolgirl who
OL,4,Cdied following house fire
OL,6,F"She was funny, charismatic, and so
OL,7,Fquick-witted - always ready with a
OL,8,Fjoke or a clever remark that brought
OL,9,Fsmiles to those around her.
OL,11,F"With an infectious energy and a heart
OL,12,Ffull of love, she had a way of making
OL,13,Fevery moment brighter.
OL,15,F"She was a true friend to so many,
OL,16,Falways bringing laughter and warmth
OL,17,Fwherever she went. She had a passion
OL,18,Ffor TikTok, makeup, and
OL,19,Fdrawing`expressing her creativity in
OL,20,Fways that made her uniquely Layla.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
