OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to schoolgirl who
OL,4,Cdied following house fire
OL,6,F"Layla was a typical, happy, and full-
OL,7,Fof-life 13-year-old, filled with
OL,8,Fdreams, laughter and love.
OL,10,F"She was cherished beyond words by her
OL,11,Fmum, dad, brothers, sisters and
OL,12,Fgrandparents who adored her deeply.
OL,14,F"She touched the hearts of everyone
OL,15,Fshe met and left a lasting impact on
OL,16,Fso many.
