OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to schoolgirl who
OL,4,Cdied following house fire
OL,6,F"We thank everyone for their kind
OL,7,Fwords and flowers. As a family we ask
OL,8,Ffor everyone to respect our privacy
OL,9,Fand leave us to grieve at this truly
OL,10,Fsad time."
OL,12,FThe fire, which began late into the
OL,13,Fevening on 2 April had been put out by
OL,14,Faround 12.30am on Thursday and
OL,15,Fneighbouring properties were checked
OL,16,Ffor fire and smoke.
